data.description: Welcome to Pungo living at its finest! This updated home offers an abundance of space on a generous one-acre lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by soaring ceilings allowing natural light to flood the rooms. Fresh paint, new LVP & carpet give the home a modern & luxurious feel. No expense spared with a state-of-the-art septic system & geothermal unit, providing eco-friendly efficiency & year-round comfort. The huge primary boasts an ensuite & equally impressive walk-in closet with a climate controlled walk-in attic. This property offers an array of spaces to suit every need. Detached oversized garage with power provides room for parking & storage. A first-floor in-law suite, full bath & private entrance is ideal for multi-generational living or hosting guests. The kitchen has a large layout, pantry & plenty of space for an island. The generator hookup, generator & security system offers additional peace of mind. Don’t miss this opportunity to make country living a reality!
